{"tid":574904,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"滑雪新手上路多問","createTime":"2018-02-27T20:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T13:40:48.000Z","uid":740,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf03f7b8a3ad6f66b1d65db5e8177aac87b45d2","tid":574904,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"小弟想玩Snowboard<br />\n<br />\n有咩裝備必買<br />\n<br />\n好想買塊板，有咩可以推介<br />\n<br />\n請問有咩好滑雪場係歐洲，皆因小弟係歐洲<br />\n<br />\n感謝回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b45f46e5d29aa4c705e316303e20168c4768ef","tid":574904,"uid":160798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:46:52.000Z","msg":"一開始就玩Snowboard好高難度喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82d31cbfcf59df5bc1b6c7290be5c9c893ddba1","tid":574904,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b45f46e5d29aa4c705e316303e20168c4768ef","tid":574904,"uid":160798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:46:52.000Z","msg":"一開始就玩Snowboard好高難度喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T22:31:37.000Z","msg":"對ski 興趣唔太大，類似嘅運動都玩過唔知有無幫助"},{"pid":"bf8a094d5ad54d2058b10714fa939a3e29ee172f","tid":574904,"uid":77545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13b45f46e5d29aa4c705e316303e20168c4768ef","tid":574904,"uid":160798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:46:52.000Z","msg":"一開始就玩Snowboard好高難度喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T22:57:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得snowboard易上手過ski<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240acf8bac8784f4b504daf73bd579b2d7641aaa","tid":574904,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:36:07.000Z","msg":"一開始邊個場都一樣<br />\n<br />\n買嘢就。。。錢多可以買曬一套先。snowboard會建議你買護具，例如wrist guard tail bone guard"},{"pid":"fece513232876047fb91421ca241b88f0e3c1cd5","tid":574904,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"一步到位啦"},{"pid":"075788c88e2edc6cb5788f6f89ec18b3107d4874","tid":574904,"uid":62344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:04:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得 板/鞋/bindings唔洗買住<br />\n去到租嚟試滑下先<br />\n一開始最重要係雪褲，雪褸，手套同護目鏡<br />\n頭盔optional 但就建議你戴頭盔"},{"pid":"7bc57bac6b833b91f1cd7fe79b6f971652ecf5c0","tid":574904,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ea6ee2dacde499057e71039c19d304f979d23d4","tid":574904,"uid":51108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:18:23.000Z","msg":"helmet租住先<br />\n如果真係鍾意玩先買equipment都唔遲<br />\n同埋買鞋真係唔好慳<br />\n<br />\n連燈有個滑雪po，有高手專玩歐洲同日本，你可以去問下<br />\n<br />\n同埋。。。而家好似係興ski多過sb。。。<br />\n<br />\n利申ski同sb都識"},{"pid":"5afa175c26396f05db24dc748afa335a76368276","tid":574904,"uid":73547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea6ee2dacde499057e71039c19d304f979d23d4","tid":574904,"uid":51108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:18:23.000Z","msg":"helmet租住先<br />\n如果真係鍾意玩先買equipment都唔遲<br />\n同埋買鞋真係唔好慳<br />\n<br />\n連燈有個滑雪po，有高手專玩歐洲同日本，你可以去問下<br />\n<br />\n同埋。。。而家好似係興ski多過sb。。。<br />\n<br />\n利申ski同sb都識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"認同買鞋唔好慳<br />\n你對腳舒唔舒服最直接影響你成個體驗<br />\n玩得唔舒服就冇癮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申, snowboard only<br />\n09年買工具用到依家，不過我諗高峰期一年先滑8次左右"},{"pid":"a750019c25082ef47b752d407a69f5d8dda9dd0f","tid":574904,"uid":51108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5afa175c26396f05db24dc748afa335a76368276","tid":574904,"uid":73547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea6ee2dacde49905